-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ph%C3%B3ng-ng%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-j1NsF-L-kuqg8ZJRLu1Sfw">Phóng ngôn kỳ 3 - 放言其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Th%C3%B4i-th%E1%BA%ADp-tam-b%C3%ACnh-s%E1%BB%B1-C%C3%B4ng-Ph%E1%BB%A5/poem-fRK8CGJbo3SFane4NSBj2A">Tặng Thôi thập tam bình sự Công Phụ - 贈崔十三評事公輔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/Th%C3%ADch-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BA%B7ng-b%E1%BA%A3o-ki%E1%BA%BFm-ca/poem-HXaql36esN3yPAO45nvb2A">Thích tướng quân tặng bảo kiếm ca - 戚將軍贈寶劍歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/author-K5yGjv4-gkyzXKfuttJFiQ">Vương Thế Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tu%C3%BD-h%E1%BA%ADu-cu%E1%BB%93ng-ng%C3%B4n-th%C3%B9-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Ti%C3%AAu-%C3%82n-nh%E1%BB%8B-hi%E1%BB%87p-lu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-9ZhJAi3DjT-FEtHvvFbdPw">Tuý hậu cuồng ngôn, thù tặng Tiêu, Ân nhị hiệp luật - 醉後狂言，酬贈蕭、殷二協律</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br></div>	</div>
